.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, june
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | milk     | iced-tea |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Birthday   | june     | august     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 